	* module/mes/M1.scm: Use it.

	mescc: Refactor decl.
	* module/language/c99/compiler.mes (decl->info, ptr-declr->pointer):
	  New function.
	  (ast->info): Use decl->info.

	guix: Update build.
	* guix.scm (mes): Do not strip.  Fixes mes binary.

	build: support Guix.
