	* mes.c (scm_t): Change car, string, ref, cdr, macro, vector into g_cell index
	  [WAS]: scm_t pointer.
	* define.c: Update.
	* lib.c: Update.
	* math.c: Update.
	* posix.c: Update.
	* quasiquote.c: Update.
