	  cache_invalidate_range): Implement cache for environment.
	  (assq_ref_cache): New function, perform cached lookups.
	  (builtin_eval,lookup_macro): Use it.
	  (set_cdr_x): Invalidate cache.
	  (set_x): Likewise.
	  (apply_env): Likewise.

